e value of this property is ","type":"text"},{"code":"YES","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" and the map is tilted, the annotation","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"view appears smaller if it is towards the top of the view (closer to the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"horizon) and larger if it is towards the bottom of the view (closer to the","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"viewpoint). This is also the behavior of "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotationImage","isActive":true},{"text":" objects. When the","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"value of this property is ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"NO"},{"text":" or the map’s pitch is zero, the annotation view","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"remains the same size regardless of its position on-screen.","type":"text"}]},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"The default value of this property is ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"NO"},{"type":"text","text":". Keep this property set to "},{"code":"NO","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" if"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"the view’s legibility is important.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"style":"note","type":"aside","name":"Note","content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Scaling many on-screen annotation views can contribute to poor map"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"performance. Consider keeping this property disabled if your use case"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"involves hundreds or thousands of annotation views.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}]}]}],"kind":"symbol","references":{"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNAnnotationView":{"fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"MLNAnnotationView"}],"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"The "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotationView","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" class is responsible for marking a point annotation"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"with a view. Annotation views represent an annotation object, which is an"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"object that corresponds to the "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotation","isActive":true,"type":"reference"},{"type":"text","text":" protocol. When an annotation’s"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"geographic coordinate is visible in the map view, the map view asks its"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"delegate to a corresponding annotation view. If an annotation view is created","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"with a reuse identifier, the map view may recycle the view when it goes"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"offscreen."}],"type":"topic","kind":"symbol","role":"symbol","title":"MLNAnnotationView","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotationView","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnannotationview"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNAnnotationImage":{"role":"symbol","title":"MLNAnnotationImage","kind":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotationImage","type":"topic","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnannotationimage","fragments":[{"text":"MLNAnnotationImage","kind":"identifier"}],"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"The "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotationImage","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"text":" class is responsible for presenting point-based","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"annotations visually on a map view. Annotation image objects wrap ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"UIImage"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"objects and may be recycled later and put into a reuse queue that is maintained"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"by the map view.","type":"text"}]},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre":{"kind":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre","role":"collection","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre","abstract":[{"text":"Powerful, free and open-source mapping toolkit with full control over data sources and styling.","type":"text"}],"type":"topic","title":"MapLibre"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNAnnotation":{"fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"MLNAnnotation"}],"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"The "},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotation"},{"type":"text","text":" protocol is used to provide annotation-related information"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"to a map view. To use this protocol, you adopt it in any custom objects that","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"store or represent annotation data. Each object then serves as the source of"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"information about a single map annotation and provides critical information,"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"such as the annotation’s location on the map. Annotation objects do not provide"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"the visual representation of the annotation but typically coordinate (in"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"conjunction with the map view’s delegate) the creation of an appropriate"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"objects to handle the display."}],"type":"topic","kind":"symbol","role":"symbol","title":"MLNAnnotation","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotation","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnannotation"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNAnnotationView/scalesWithViewingDista